                                 .: MCD's Colloide v0.9 :.
				    
MCD's Colloide version 0.9 // 2017 // Thessaloniki, Greece

What it is about:
Colloide is an extremely simple information gathering tool with the solid purpose of finding working admin login web-pages. 

Language:  Python
version:   0.9
Code:      Open source
License:   GNU GPL

  				 _.:' VERSION DIARY ':._

